  "A derivative measures the instantaneous rate of change of a function at a given point. Geometrically, it represents the slope of the tangent line to the curve at that point.": "衍生物测量一个函数在某一点的瞬时变化速率。从几何角度来说,它代表该点向曲线的正切线的斜度。",
  "What does the sum/difference rule for derivatives state?": "衍生物的总和/差异规则是什么?",
